ZH: 我们在这个特殊的日子里缅怀着那些为国家做出贡献的先辈。
EN: On this special day, we remember and honor the ancestors who contributed to our country.

ZH: 他们缅怀着那段艰难的回忆，但也感激那里的成长经历。
EN: They reminisce about that difficult period but also appreciate the experiences they had there.

ZH: 缅怀人民英雄，是我们的责任和义务。
EN: Remembering the heroes of the people is our responsibility and duty.

ZH: 他们在母校门前停下脚步，缅怀着曾经的学生时代。
EN: They stop in front of their alma mater and reminisce about their student days.

ZH: 我们缅怀着那些为实现世界和平而付出生命的士兵们。
EN: We remember and honor the soldiers who sacrificed their lives for world peace.

ZH: 缅怀过去的同时，我们也要积极面对未来。
EN: While remembering the past, we should also actively face the future.

ZH: 每年的今天，我们都会到公墓缅怀亲人们。
EN: Every year on this day, we go to the cemetery to remember our loved ones.

ZH: 缅怀老一辈领导人的伟大事迹，能够激励我们更加奋发向前。
EN: Remembering the great achievements of the older generation of leaders can inspire us to work harder.

ZH: 通过缅怀英雄们，我们能够铭记他们的精神，继续努力为国家做贡献。
EN: By remembering the heroes, we can keep their spirit alive and continue to contribute to our nation.

ZH: 缅怀亡友，是我们减轻悲伤的一种方式。
EN: Remembering deceased friends is one way to ease our sadness.

ZH: 缅怀历史可以让我们更好地珍惜和利用现在的机会。
EN: Reflecting on history can help us better cherish and utilize present opportunities.

ZH: 我们要缅怀那些为科学事业作出巨大贡献的科学家们。
EN: We should remember and honor the scientists who have made significant contributions to the field of science.

ZH: 缅怀先烈是我们承担历史责任的一种表现。
EN: Remembering the martyrs is a way for us to shoulder our historical responsibilities.

ZH: 缅怀过去的同时，我们也要学会放下，继续向前。
EN: While remembering the past, we should also learn to let go and move forward.

ZH: 缅怀是对逝者的一种尊敬和纪念。
EN: Remembering is a way to show respect and commemorate the departed.

ZH: 在这庄严的场合，我们缅怀那些为国家建设付出努力的人们。
EN: In this solemn occasion, we remember and honor those who have contributed to the construction of our nation.

ZH: 参观历史博物馆能让我们更直观地缅怀过去的时代。
EN: Visiting historical museums allows us to have a more tangible experience of recalling the past eras.

ZH: 缅怀过去的成就能够激励我们追求更伟大的目标。
EN: Remembering past achievements can inspire us to pursue greater goals.

ZH: 推出这个专辑是为了缅怀已故的音乐巨星。
EN: Releasing this album is to commemorate the late music icon.

ZH: 我们缅怀那些为社会进步作出贡献的杰出人物。
EN: We remember and honor the outstanding individuals who have contributed to social progress.
